Company Overview of Bertolet Capital Trust - Pinnacle Value Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Bertolet Capital Trust - Pinnacle Value Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Bertolet Capital LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in value stocks of small-cap and micro-cap companies with market capitalization of less than $1 billion. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis along with a bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors such as catalysts, interest rates, strong balance sheets, capable management, attractive business niches, ownership of valuable franchises or trade names, sound ...
Bertolet Capital Trust - Pinnacle Value Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Bertolet Capital LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in value stocks of small-cap and micro-cap companies with market capitalization of less than $1 billion. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis along with a bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors such as catalysts, interest rates, strong balance sheets, capable management, attractive business niches, ownership of valuable franchises or trade names, sound accounting practices, large insider ownership, price-to-earnings, price-to-cash flow, and price-to-book multiples to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2000 Index. Bertolet Capital Trust - Pinnacle Value Fund was formed on April 1, 2003 and is domiciled in the United States.
