1788 Capital Trust S.A.
 





 

Links

Company Website



Who we are
1788 Capital Trust S.A. is a privately owned Swiss investment management firm, based in Geneva and with a representative office in London. Dedicated to very affluent individuals and Families, Trusts, Foundations, Life Insurance Policies and Private Pension Funds, the firm offers best-in-class Asset Management, Tax & Estate Planning and Multi-family Office services to a worldwide clientele. Our goal is to provide our clients fully independent investment advisory services, in a fully ethical manner ensuring excellence in operations and protection of clients’ privacy. 1788 Capital Trust is registered with the Swiss Regulatory Organization for Asset Managers – OARG – , a self-regulatory organization recognized by the FINMA.
What we do
1788 Capital Trust S.A. investment philosophy of capital preservation, absolute return strategy and open architecture, coupled with corporate values of Trust, Quality and Excellence, enable the company to hold a distinctive position within the Swiss, EU and Global markets, and is achieved without any conflict of interests. The global strategy is defined by 1788 Capital Trust Investment Advisory Board, comprising accomplished professionals and then the Investment Committee develops an asset allocation with a selection of products optimizing the performance of each asset class. The investment strategy is implemented in an optimum combination of direct investments in bonds, equities, alternative investments, structured products or optio ns. Our Team has a strong expertise in the field of alternative investments. Our approach remains a Tailor made philosophy in order to adapt the strategy to the clients requirements.


